## Behavior Matrix

| Scenario                                        | Before            | After                      |
| ----------------------------------------------- | ----------------- | -------------------------- |
| Changelog + version bump                        | ✅ `--all` commit | ✅ `--all` commit          |
| **Changelog + no version bump** (bug)           | ❌ Skipped        | ✅ Commit (changelog only) |
| No changelog + version bump                     | ✅ `--all` commit | ✅ `--all` commit          |
| No changelog + no version bump + preRelease ran | ✅ reportError    | ✅ reportError             |
| No changelog + no version bump + no preRelease  | ❌ Misleading log | ✅ Debug log (no-op)       |
